Instruction: With the module still wired as in the current configuration and all switches commanded ON, open the panel of Control Module 3 and use a multimeter to measure: (1) continuity across the switch terminals; (2) voltage across the red indicator LED/resistor branch. This will determine whether the internal series path from the input pair to the output pair is open inside the module even though the input pair has 12 V.
